65
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:29,120
In summary, that's five, five, three, three, three.

66
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:31,280
As for the rest, the junk cards, the more you get the better.

67
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:32,800
You won't really get it until you play, so??

68
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,160
- The more you get the better? - Yes, yes.

69
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,600
That's enough of an explanation.

70
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:37,400
That's it?

71
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,080
You don't learn go-stop by listening to the rules.

