00:49:02,640 --> 00:49:03,640
Right?

652
00:49:03,640 --> 00:49:07,040
The enigmatic artist who captured hallyu star Cha Si-an's heart.

653
00:49:07,040 --> 00:49:09,000
Man??I really wonder who she is.

