00:51:46,920 --> 00:51:48,000
Chairwoman.

683
00:51:49,680 --> 00:51:50,840
Mother.

684
00:51:50,840 --> 00:51:51,840
Hyo-jin?

685
00:51:51,840 --> 00:51:55,040
This is the goods,

686
00:51:55,040 --> 00:51:57,160
I mean, art merchandise I came up with myself.

687
00:51:57,160 --> 00:52:00,640
Okay, I got it. You can leave.

688
00:52:00,640 --> 00:52:02,640
And Hyo-jin?

689
00:52:02,640 --> 00:52:06,040
You're not someone who should be doing that kind of work.

690
00:52:06,040 --> 00:52:08,760
My darling Hyo-jin, you are TK's??

691
00:52:08,760 --> 00:52:10,400
I'm the daughter you've practically given up on.

692
00:52:17,080 --> 00:52:20,080
The one to whom you can give a credit card so she won't annoy you

693
00:52:20,080 --> 00:52:21,720
and who only does as you ask.

694
00:52:23,000 --> 00:52:24,000
Hyo-jin??

