00:52:24,720 --> 00:52:27,920
How come you've never asked me, Mother?

696
00:52:28,880 --> 00:52:31,400
What I like,

697
00:52:31,400 --> 00:52:33,680
or what I want to do.

698
00:52:33,680 --> 00:52:36,120
Why aren't you curious about those kinds of things?

699
00:52:36,120 --> 00:52:38,120
I find myself curious about those whom I like.

700
00:52:41,000 --> 00:52:44,880
Hyo-jin. Is there anything??

701
00:52:48,600 --> 00:52:50,080
I don't know about you?

702
00:52:50,640 --> 00:52:54,520
This??I made this.

