00:52:56,560 --> 00:53:00,000
a task I could do well.

705
00:53:00,000 --> 00:53:02,480
Curator Yoo helped me,

706
00:53:02,480 --> 00:53:04,640
and Mr. Yoo-sub cheered me on.

