00:53:04,640 --> 00:53:07,000
And Director??

708
00:53:10,800 --> 00:53:14,480
Anyway, I want to keep doing this.

709
00:53:14,480 --> 00:53:16,200
Not because of Cha Si-an,

710
00:53:16,200 --> 00:53:18,160
but because I've come to like this job!

711
00:53:22,040 --> 00:53:24,920
Even if that's so,

712
00:53:24,920 --> 00:53:26,840
