00:54:10,400 --> 00:54:12,800
One that proves no parents can win against their children.

721
00:54:26,840 --> 00:54:28,760
Do you think the special exhibit will happen?

722
00:54:30,960 --> 00:54:32,480
- Director? - Yeah.

