753
00:57:28,000 --> 00:57:30,200
Oh what? Mom, what happened?

754
00:57:33,320 --> 00:57:35,120
My son??

755
00:57:35,120 --> 00:57:36,400
Why've you grown so thin?

756
00:57:36,400 --> 00:57:37,520
When did you get here?

