789
01:00:11,160 --> 01:00:14,200
- So that's why??- That's why I come back to this.

790
01:00:16,200 --> 01:00:19,760
It was all because of Lee Sol's art,

791
01:00:19,760 --> 01:00:22,000
so I thought something might change

792
01:00:22,000 --> 01:00:24,000
if I collected all of her works.

793
01:00:29,120 --> 01:00:30,160
But you know??

794
01:00:32,480 --> 01:00:34,880
I've actually seen this painting before.

795
01:00:38,440 --> 01:00:40,040
Not three years ago,

796
01:00:42,000 --> 01:00:43,480
but further back in the past.

797
01:00:49,160 --> 01:00:51,000
When I was very young.

798
01:00:54,320 --> 01:00:56,040
By young you mean??

799
01:00:58,760 --> 01:01:00,600
Before I was Ryan.

800
01:01:02,480 --> 01:01:04,400
When I was Heo Yun-je.

801
01:01:11,600 --> 01:01:13,960
I saw her paint that.

802
01:01:16,200 --> 01:01:18,080
If you saw it being painted, then??

803
01:01:20,120 --> 01:01:22,240
Lee Sol's painting is??

